    <Statements>
      <Statement>Partition shapes into parts with equal areas. Express the area of each part as a unit fraction of the whole. &lt;i&gt;For example, partition a shape into 4 parts with equal area, and describe the area of each part as 1/4 of the area of the shape&lt;/i&gt;.</Statement>
